Let $E$ and $F$ be the tangency points of the incircle on $AC$ and $AB$.
By angle chasing,
\[ \angle PIF = \angle AIF - \angle AIP
  = \left( 90\dg - \half \angle A \right) - \half \angle B = \half \angle C. \]
