\[ \angle BA_1C + \angle CB_1A + \angle AC_1B = 480\dg. \]
Let $A_2 = \ol{BC_1} \cap \ol{CB_1}$, $B_2 = \ol{CA_1} \cap \ol{AC_1}$,
